            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6415222,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 天瀚(6225)急跌-6.94%報22.2元，成交3張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>天瀚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6225:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6225\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6225-TW</a>)近5分K跌速6.94%，10日12:30報22.2元，成交3張，今日漲幅為9.36％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>天瀚(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6225:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6225\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6225-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲4.64%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-4 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-3 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
